Detailed Viva Questions and Answers

Practical 1 Viva Answers

What is Data Wrangling?

Process of cleaning and transforming raw data into useful format.

Why is data cleaning necessary?

To improve data quality and remove errors.

What is DataFrame?

A two-dimensional tabular structure in Pandas.

What does head() do?

Displays first 5 rows of dataset.

What does describe() do?

Provides statistical summary like mean, min, max.

What is dropna()?

Removes rows containing null values.

What is fillna()?

Fills missing values with specified values.


